---
import '../../styles/global.css';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import GoogleHead from "../../components/GoogleHead.astro";
import settings from "../../settings";
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>HVAC Careers | Bell County, TX</title>
	<meta name="description"
	      content="Join our team at Alltek Services. We're always looking for new talent and seasoned experts in the HVAC industry. Competitive pay and benefits.">
	<GoogleHead/>
</head>

<body class="bg-white text-gray-800">
<Header/>

<main>
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-primary text-white">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 font-heading">CAREERS AT ALLTEK SERVICES</h1>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Main Content -->
	<section class="py-16 px-4">
		<div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl">
			<div class="mb-12">
				<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">HVAC Jobs in Bell County & Surrounding Areas</h2>
				<div class="prose max-w-none">
					<p class="text-lg mb-4">
						The HVAC industry is always looking for new talent and seasoned experts. If you're ready to bring your
						talents to the people of Bell County, Alltek Services has a home for you. We're always ready to expand our
						team, train apprentices, and help our neighbors build a rewarding and fulfilling career right in their own
						backyard.
					</p>
					<p class="text-lg mb-4">
						Alltek Services believes in putting people first, and that doesn't just apply to our customers â€“ we treat
						our employees like family and ensure they're well taken care of. And by assembling and nurturing the best
						possible team, we make sure that our customers get the best possible care.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Why Work for Alltek Section -->
			<div class="mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-8">WHY WORK FOR ALLTEK SERVICES?</h2>

				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
					<div>
						<ul class="space-y-4">
							<li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-accent mr-3">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                         stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                            d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
								<span class="text-lg">We have over 30 years of field experience</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-accent mr-3">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                         stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                            d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
								<span class="text-lg">We're an established company within our community</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-accent mr-3">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                         stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                            d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
								<span class="text-lg">We value honesty and integrity</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div>
						<ul class="space-y-4">
							<li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-accent mr-3">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                         stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                            d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
								<span class="text-lg">We support the development of our team</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-accent mr-3">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                         stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                            d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
								<span class="text-lg">We provide competitive pay and benefits</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-accent mr-3">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                         stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                            d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
								<span class="text-lg">We hire technicians from and service customers in countless communities across Bell County and the surrounding areas</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg">
					<p class="text-lg">
						To learn more about our employee benefits, training programs, and current employment opportunities, call our
						Bell County office at <a href={`tel:${settings.phoneRaw}`}
						                         class="text-accent font-bold hover:underline">{settings.phone}</a> or <a
						href="/contact" class="text-accent font-bold hover:underline">get in touch with us online</a> today!
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- What Sets Alltek Apart Section -->
			<div class="mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-8">WHAT SETS ALLTEK SERVICES APART?</h2>

				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
					<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md text-center">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
							     stroke="currentColor">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6v6m0 0v6m0-6h6m-6 0H6"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">30+ YEARS OF EXPERIENCE</h3>
						<p>Decades of industry knowledge and expertise to support your growth.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md text-center">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
							     stroke="currentColor">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
								      d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">MAINTENANCE PLANS & FINANCING OFFERED</h3>
						<p>We provide solutions that help our customers and create steady work for our team.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md text-center">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
							     stroke="currentColor">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
								      d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/>
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
								      d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">LOCALLY OWNED & OPERATED</h3>
						<p>We're invested in our community and the people who live and work here.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- CTA Section -->
			<div class="text-center">
				<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">JOIN OUR TEAM TODAY</h2>
				<p class="text-lg mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
					Ready to start your career with a company that values its employees and provides opportunities for growth?
					Contact us today to learn about our current openings.
				</p>
				<a href="/contact" rel="noreferrer"
				   class="bg-accent hover:bg-accent/90 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-md font-bold text-lg inline-flex items-center transition-colors">
					Apply Now
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd"
						      d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
						      clip-rule="evenodd"/>
					</svg>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</main>

<Footer/>
</body>
</html>
